race.comment: DOUBLE RAP (8) finished 15 lengths away in sixth last time out over 1207m at this track three weeks ago. Tackles a longer journey this time. The one to beat in this line up. GOSPEL JOURNEY (7) improved last start to finish second over 1673m at this track after being prominent at the corner. Faces an easier assignment so he is a major player. DOUBLE R CAT (2) is racing well and is close to a win, the latest effort a solid third at this track (Dirt) over 1673m after being in contention all the way. Drawn to stalk the leaders. Finds an easier assignment and can get the job done. CHAHTA CITIZEN (6) is finding the breakthrough elusive, beaten 28 lengths into sixth at his latest appearance over 1673m at this track (Dirt). Leading prospect on best form.
